@startuml
title Echoes of the Hollow Crown - Ideology Clash System

' =========================
' CORE IDEOLOGIES
' =========================

package "Core Ideologies" {

[Truth at any cost\n(Kael's path)] as I1
[Security through Ignorance\n(Anchor Wardens)] as I2
[Freedom through Forgetting\n(Veil Rememberers)] as I3
[Rebirth through Reunion\n(Shard Cult)] as I4
[Peace through Hollowing\n(Hollow Order)] as I5

}

' =========================
' DIRECT CONFLICTS
' =========================

I1 -[#red]-> I2 : "Truth vs Safety"
I1 -[#red]-> I3 : "Remembering vs Erasing"
I1 -[#red]-> I4 : "Individual truth vs Collective ascension"
I1 -[#red]-> I5 : "Life with pain vs Emptiness"

I2 -[#red]-> I3 : "Memory as duty vs Memory as curse"
I2 -[#red]-> I5 : "Controlled ignorance vs Forced emptiness"

I3 -[#red]-> I4 : "Gentle forgetting vs Violent rebirth"
I3 -[#red]-> I5 : "Voluntary erasure vs Forced Hollowing"

I4 -[#red]-> I5 : "Ascension for all vs Sacrifice of many"

' =========================
' FACTION & CHARACTER ASSOCIATIONS
' =========================

[Anchor Wardens] as Wardens
[Veil Rememberers] as Rememberers
[Shard Cult] as Cult
[Hollow Order] as HollowOrder
[Kael Voss] as Kael

Wardens --> I2
Rememberers --> I3
Cult --> I4
HollowOrder --> I5
Kael --> I1 : "Evolving path"

' =========================
' IDEOLOGY EVOLUTION
' =========================

[Old Mira (Early)] as MiraE
[Old Mira (Later)] as MiraL

MiraE --> I2 : "Protect the village"
MiraL --> I5 : "Better Hollow than another Cataclysm"

[Kael (Chapter 1)] as KaelEarly
[Kael (Final)] as KaelFinal

KaelEarly --> I2 : "Believes in the tithe"
KaelFinal --> I1 : "Seeks painful truth"

' =========================
' FINAL CONVERGENCE
' =========================

[Final Question:\nCan truth be embraced without repeating Veyra's hubris?\nIs any "peace" worth the cost of identity?] as Final

I1 --> Final
I2 --> Final
I3 --> Final
I4 --> Final
I5 --> Final

@enduml